  • Constructor Details

    • Courses

      public Courses(String courseName, String groupId, String courseCreditsMin, String courseCreditsMax, Boolean booleanValue, Boolean credits_added)
      Constructs a Courses objects with the CourseUnit info such as course name, course id, course minimum credits and course maximum credits. It also takes a Boolean value which will be used to determine whether the student has marked the CourseUnit as completed or not.
      Parameters:
      courseName - - name of the CourseUnit.
      groupId - - groupId of the CourseUnit.
      courseCreditsMin - - minimum credits of the CourseUnit.
      courseCreditsMax - - maximum credits of the CourseUnit.
      booleanValue - - Boolean value.
